\r\n\r\nThis comes with the python 3 plugin BTW which good for me as that's my scripting language of choice.", "distro": "Fedora", "karma_down": 0, "karma_up": 1, "locale": "en_US", "rating": 100, "reported": 0, "review_id": 5203, "score": 0, "summary": "Simple to use but easy enough to add features through scripting", "user_display": null, "version": "2.12.4"}, {"app_id": "hexchat.desktop", "date_created": 1543024097.0, "description": "I'm getting errors that the package not available on CentOS 7.5? It works fine on Fedora but will not install on CentOS?", "distro": "CentOS Linux", "karma_down": 0, "karma_up": 0, "locale": "en_US", "rating": 20, "reported": 0, "review_id": 10845, "score": 0, "summary": "CentOS Hexchat", "user_display": "Iron Geeks", "version": "unknown"}, {"app_id": "hexchat.desktop", "date_created": 1554654203.0, "description": "Sim, funciona bem! Este deveria substituir o \"Polari\" que \u00e9 nativo do Gnome.", "distro": "Debian GNU/Linux", "karma_down": 0, "karma_up": 0, "locale": "en_US", "rating": 100, "reported": 0, "review_id": 19226, "score": 0, "summary": "Funciona!", "user_display": "voyager1", "version": "2.12.4"}, {"app_id": "io.github.Hexchat.desktop", "date_created": 1494593395.0, "description": "Polari doesn't work and Konversation doesn't look good in GNOME, but HexChat works and looks okay.", "distro": "Debian GNU/Linux", "karma_down": 18, "karma_up": 46, "locale": "en_US", "rating": 100, "reported": 0, "review_id": 3165, "score": 0, "summary": "The best IRC", "user_display": "ivans", "version": "master"}, {"app_id": "io.github.Hexchat.desktop", "date_created": 1539676072.0, "description": "It's never once failed on me and it's cross platform. Dazzling amount of settings and menus, but ages of reliable use make up for that.", "distro": "Debian GNU/Linux", "karma_down": 1, "karma_up": 1, "locale": "en_GB", "rating": 100, "reported": 0, "review_id": 9807, "score": 0, "summary": "Reliable", "user_display": "Computer", "version": "2.1